          "type": "text",
          "text": "USP_NoteRetrieve",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve notes from a view named "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Common.vwNotes",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " based on various optional filtering criteria. It logs the retrieval action, including any exceptions encountered during execution, into an application log using another stored procedure "
